<h1>佛</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#cc7700;">fú</span><span class=alesi>(fu2)</span> , <span style="color:#cc7700;">fó</span><span class=alesi>(fo2)</span> , <span style="color:#cc7700;">bó</span><span class=alesi>(bo2)</span> , <span style="color:#000099;">bì</span><span class=alesi>(bi4)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 佛 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 佛</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/Buddha" style="color:black;">Buddha</a>; <a href="/dictionary/of" style="color:black;">of</a> <a href="/dictionary/Buddhism" style="color:black;">Buddhism</a>; merciful person; Buddhist image; the dead (Jap.)</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 7<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 7 strokes: <a href="/character/我" title="wo3: our, us, i, me, my, we">我</a>, <a href="/character/这" title="zhe4: this, the, here">这</a>, <a href="/character/来" title="lai2: come, coming; return, returning">来</a>, <a href="/character/时" title="shi2: time, season; era, age, period">时</a>, <a href="/character/你" title="ni3: you, second person pronoun">你</a>, <a href="/character/作" title="zuo4: make; work; compose, write; act, perform">作</a>, <a href="/character/里" title="li3: unit of distance; village; lane">里</a>, <a href="/character/没" title="mei2: not, have not, none; drown, sink">没</a>, <a href="/character/还" title="hai2: still, yet, also, besides">还</a>, <a href="/character/进" title="jin4: advance, make progress, enter">进</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/人" title="Kangxi radical 9">人</a>&nbsp;9.5</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 5 <br><small>Other HSK 5 characters: <a href="/character/宣" title="xuan1: declare, announce, proclaim">宣</a>, <a href="/character/追" title="zhui1: pursue, chase after; expel">追</a>, <a href="/character/执" title="zhi2: hold in hand; keep; carry out">执</a>, <a href="/character/控" title="kong4: accuse, charge; control">控</a>, <a href="/character/税" title="shui4: taxes">税</a>, <a href="/character/背" title="bei4: back; back side; behind; betray">背</a>, <a href="/character/阵" title="zhen4: column, row or file of troops">阵</a>, <a href="/character/恶" title="e4: evil, wicked, bad, foul">恶</a>, <a href="/character/善" title="shan4: good, virtuous, charitable, kind">善</a>, <a href="/character/顿" title="dun4: pause, stop; bow, kowtow; arrange">顿</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-5" title="List o